      <title>加拿大住房部长辞去特鲁多内阁职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-s-housing-minister-resigns-from-trudeau-s-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大住房部长肖恩·弗雷泽 (Sean Fraser) 将辞去内阁职务，并且不打算参加下次选举。2025 年大选迫在眉睫，贾斯汀·特鲁多 (Justin Trudeau) 领导的自由党在民意调查中支持率低迷，因此他做出了这一决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/canada-s-housing-minister-resigns-from-trudeau-s-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 02:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国房价下跌速度放缓，复苏“脆弱”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-home-prices-fall-at-slower-pace-in-fragile-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11 月份中国房价跌幅连续第三个月收窄，表明随着政策制定者加大力度结束房地产市场低迷，房价开始企稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/china-home-prices-fall-at-slower-pace-in-fragile-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 01:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grab 本季度表现亮眼，部分分析师预计其股价将进一步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/grab-s-big-quarter-has-some-analysts-seeing-further-stock-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Grab Holdings Ltd. 削减成本和在东南亚叫车服务领域击败竞争对手的能力，推动其本季度股价表现超越全球同行，一些分析师表示未来还将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/grab-s-big-quarter-has-some-analysts-seeing-further-stock-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 01:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
